      <h2>Fast help when an electrical issue feels unsafe</h2>
      <p>Electrical problems can change quickly. A breaker that trips again and again, a hot outlet, a burning smell, or flickering lights can point to a circuit, device, wiring, or panel problem that needs careful attention.</p>
      <p>Fateh Plumbing & Electric helps Brampton customers with urgent electrical troubleshooting, breaker issues, dead outlets, failed switches, partial power loss, lighting problems, damaged wiring, and panel concerns. We also help decide whether a problem needs immediate attention or can be scheduled safely.</p>
      <p>When you call, tell us what happened, which room or circuit is affected, whether you smelled burning, saw sparks, heard buzzing, or noticed water near electrical equipment. Clear details help the technician arrive prepared.</p>
